track.name: Russian Mind
comments: probably the best song I can think of consisting only of a single synth arpeggio. Lopatin is a genius.
Oh my god. This is THE music to listen to while riding on an airplane.

Love from first second.
P.S. Now I'm really proud of being russian :)
